<em>transform</em> them. And in that example, just stay with it. Look at it.</p>

<blockquote>
  <p>Ah! Being critical. Yes, I can sure be critical. I‚Äôve been that way in
the past. I know that energy very well.</p>
</blockquote>

<p>Look upon a scene in your memory in which <em>you</em> have been the one being
critical. Look upon it with deep honesty and sincerity, and say to
