<blockquote>
  <p>I forgive me for being critical. I forgive my judgment of myself. I
choose to teach only Love.</p>
</blockquote>

<p>Watch that image disappear from your mind, dissolve from your mind. And
bring it back to the present moment and that person that just pushed
