<blockquote>
  <p>How have I ever wanted to drive a nail through someone else?</p>
</blockquote>

<p>And I remembered my murderous thoughts. I forgave myself and brought my
attention back to that one, and asked only to see the Light in him. And
I asked,</p>

<blockquote>
  <p>What is it that this action is mirroring to me? What is it masking
