</blockquote>

<p>And I saw that one‚Äôs soul, and I loved that one‚Äôs soul. And I felt
compassion for that one. And in that moment ‚Äî mark my words ‚Äî in that
moment of eye contact, that one got it!</p>

<p>Because my energy was different, it created the space in which that soul
